  "time_ut": 1658490528,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u2018\u2018\u0d85\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dbd\u0dba\u0da7 \u0d91\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd \u0d9a\u0dc5 \u0db8\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dbb\u0dd2 \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dc4\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dba \u0dc4\u0dd9\u0dc5\u0dcf \u0daf\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf\u2018\u2018",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\"Condemns the military attack on the struggle\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Karu Jayasuriya, Chairman of the National Movement for a Just Society, states that he strongly condemns the military attack on the Galle mouth struggle community.",
        "Mr. Karu Jayasuriya said in a statement that he is requesting all sections of the population to rally in order to create an environment that does not allow such heinous acts.",
        "\"The attack by the security forces targeting the Galle mouth struggle community, which has brought the politics of this country to a critical turning point, should be strongly condemned by every party that appreciates and aspires to democracy in the country. The National Movement for a Just Society also strongly condemns the same action.",
        "In a democratic society, the right to hold different opinions and to express one's views as well as to protest peacefully should be protected from the highest level. We must all admit that no social column can engage in solitary struggles apart from the aspirations of the common society. The Galle mouth struggle was very active because of that reason. The rulers of this country should understand that even a ruler who had unlimited power in the history of Sri Lanka after independence left the country and ran away for the first time because that struggle and the aspirations of the people coincided.",
        "According to our records, the militants were preparing to leave the President's Office today. If so, it can be considered as the most intelligent and correct decision taken by them. No party can justify this inhumane attack in such an environment.",
        "This incident also shows the unwillingness or inability of our country's political society to resolve crises and differences in a civilized manner. Eliminating this culture from the country is the responsibility of the entire society and for that the political authority of the country should take the lead before everyone else.",
        "Therefore, we earnestly request the entire society of this country to come forward with determination to free the country from the tragic situation that it is facing today, and to unite to create an environment that does not allow such heinous acts."
      ],
